<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,address=no,email=no">
    <title>Your Account Credentials</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #0A0A0A;
            background-color: #F4F4F5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .wrapper {
            background-color: #F4F4F5;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 560px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #171717;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 28px 32px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #FAFAFA;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 36px 32px 28px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111111;
            margin: 0 0 8px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #71717A;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 0 0 28px;
        }
        .id-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #F4F4F5;
            border: 1px solid #E4E4E7;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #3F3F46;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .id-badge span {
            color: #A1A1AA;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-right: 4px;
        }
        /* Credentials card */
        .cred-card {
            background-color: #18181B;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .cred-row {
            padding: 18px 22px;
        }
        .cred-row + .cred-row {
            border-top: 1px solid #27272A;
        }
        .cred-label {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.2px;
            color: #71717A;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .cred-value {
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #FAFAFA;
            word-break: break-all;
            /* prevent email clients from auto-linking */
            color: #FAFAFA !important;
            text-decoration: none !important;
        }
        .cred-password {
            font-size: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            color: #A3E635 !important;
        }
        /* Button */
        .btn-wrap {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #171717;
            color: #FFFFFF !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 13px 32px;
            border-radius: 7px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
        }
        /* Alert */
        .alert {
            background-color: #FFFBEB;
            border: 1px solid #FCD34D;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .alert-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #92400E;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .alert-body {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #A16207;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid #F0F0F0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        /* Security tips */
        .tips-title {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.8px;
            color: #A1A1AA;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .tips-list {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 18px;
        }
        .tips-list li {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #52525B;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .tips-list li:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .error-note {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #A1A1AA;
            margin: 20px 0 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #FAFAFA;
            border-top: 1px solid #F0F0F0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 18px 32px;
        }
        .footer p {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #A1A1AA;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Employee Management System</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="greeting">Welcome, {{employeeName}}</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Your account is ready. Use the credentials below to sign in for the first time.</p>

            <div class="id-badge">
                <span>Employee ID</span>{{employeeId}}
            </div>

            <div class="cred-card">
                <div class="cred-row">
                    <div class="cred-label">Login Email</div>
                    <div class="cred-value">{{email}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="cred-row">
                    <div class="cred-label">Temporary Password</div>
                    <div class="cred-value cred-password">{{temporaryPassword}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="btn-wrap">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="cta-button">Sign In to Your Account</a>
            </div>

            <div class="alert">
                <div class="alert-title">Change your password on first sign-in</div>
                <p class="alert-body">This is a temporary password. You will be asked to set a new one when you log in for the first time.</p>
            </div>

            <hr class="divider">

            <div class="tips-title">Keep your account secure</div>
            <ul class="tips-list">
                <li>Never share your password with anyone, including IT or HR</li>
                <li>Use at least 8 characters with uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and symbols</li>
                <li>Do not reuse passwords from other accounts</li>
                <li>Contact IT immediately if you suspect unauthorized access</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="error-note">If you were not expecting this email, please contact HR or IT support right away.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message from the Employee Management System.</p>
            <p>Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
